name: Rectangle Verena Purple Geometric 2' x 3' Area Rug for Entryway, Living Room, Dinning Room, etc.
shortDescription:
Rectangle Verena Purple Geometric 2' x 3' Area Rug for Entryway, Living Room, Dinning Room, etc. Description:
The Solana Collection represents a Retro Modern vibe and the L'Baiet Verena Purple Geometric Rug embodies this. Its fun nostalgia comes alive in colorful hues of purple and greys. This rug pairs well with Mid-Century Modern furniture. Power-loomed in Turkey from a combination of polypropylene and polyester, this stain and fade resistant rug is great for high foot traffic areas in your home. Maintenance of this rug is made easy; animal hairs and lint don't easily adhere to the fibers making vacuuming a breeze. When vacuuming adjust the beater bar and brush at the highest setting as to avoid excess wear. For stains spot clean only with mild detergent and water or have it professionally removed if necessary. We recommend the use of a non-skid pad to keep the rug in place on smooth surfaces. In addition, the pile height of this rug is ideal for placing under your living room furniture creating a cozy and inviting space in your home. Power-loomed from a blend of polypropylene and polyester ensuring durability for years to come. Generous 0.43 inch pile height with high low effect provides ample comfort yet seamless for placement underneath furniture. Machine made construction that is stain resistant, fade resistant and doesn't shed. Recommended for residential indoor use in any room of your home. Vacuum when needed. If spills occur, spot clean with mild detergent. Made in Turkey. Warranty: Manufacturer limited 90 Days warranty covers any defects in material or workmanship under normal use during the warranty period. Guarantee does not provide replacement necessitated by normal wear-and-tear, misuse or accidental damage.
